Stuff being implemented.

Functionnal
- Parsing content with Textile, Markdown, ReStructuredText and Liquid
- Helpers ( Link / Menu / Asset / Breadcrumbs )
- widgets (categories, tags, links, facebook, twitter, etc)
- RSS feeds
- Sitemap
- Multilingual
- Google Analytics
- Google Webmaster Toolkit
- Generating a temporary index.html "Website is being updated" for live updates
- Migration script from well known CMS
- Compass for CSS
- Assetic for assets
- Comments.php for commenting pages (comments.js frontside)
- A standard set of template files

Internal 
- Unit tests
- use Monolog to log objects behavior (whether than useless //echo)
- Integrated webserver for live-viewing
- Metadata parser: let the user know when he's not using an official metadata

Doc
- Howto run on linux/mac/windows
- Typical create/write/publish loop
